{
  "texts": [
    "We are doing a deal where we are staffing 20 people at one of our clients.",
    "It might make sense to look into, for example, how often our consultants are going to be at the client location.",
    "What kind of commutes are they doing?",
    "But also, they have 40 hours per week, their laptop running for this particular client.",
    "So, coming up with a report that provides some level of details in terms of, e.g., carbon footprint, but maybe also on how often they need to change their laptops and what kind of resources are impacted by that, whatever."
  ]
}